data.title: Ancestors of Eugene Ashton ANDREW & Anna Louise HANISH Princess Anastasia Yaroslavna KIEV ANDREW ANGERMUELLER HANISH STRUDELL Decendants
data.text:
Princess of KIEV.

BOOKS

Kings and Queens of Europe, Genealogical Chart, Anne Taute and Romilly Squire, Taute 1989: "Andras I, Son of Vaszoly Laslo, King of Hungary or Magyarorszag 1047-1060, Mar Anastasia Daughter of Yaroslav Grand Prince of Kiev."

ANCESTRAL FILE

Ancestral File Ver 4.10 881C-RD Anastaziya KIEV Princess Born Abt 1023, 952M-VX Anastasiya Agmunda Yaroslavna KIEV Born Abt 1035, Ancestral File Ver 4.10 952M-VX Born 1023, Ver 4.19 952M-VX Born Abt 1035.

Anastasia married King Andras Magyarorszag HUNGARY, I, son of Prince Vaszoly Laslo Magyarorszag HUNGARY, about 1037. (King Andras Magyarorszag HUNGARY, I was born in 1001 in Esztergom, Esztergom, Megye, Hungary, died after 6 Jul 1060 in Zircz, Veszprem, Hungary and was buried in Tihany, Veszprem, Hungary.)
